items.name: Thread of Hope
explicitMods: Only affects Passives in Large Ring
Passives in Radius can be Allocated without being connected to your tree
-20% to all Elemental Resistances
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: Though we cannot touch; one thought, one wish, through centuries alone in darkness.

items.name: Forbidden Flame
explicitMods: Allocates Vile Bastion if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flesh
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The minds of those studied utterly by the Cleansing Fire
continue to think and dream and beg for silence...

items.name: Megalomaniac
explicitMods: Adds 4 Passive Skills
Added Small Passive Skills grant Nothing
1 Added Passive Skill is Enduring Composure
1 Added Passive Skill is Pure Guile
1 Added Passive Skill is Titanic Swings
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Medium or Large Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Added passives do not interact with jewel radiuses. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: If you're going to act like you're better than everyone else, make sure you are.

items.name: Impossible Escape
explicitMods:
Passives in Radius of Unwavering Stance can be Allocated
without being connected to your tree
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: She was the last of countless progeny bred to test the limits of limitless power.
In the cosmic prison of her birth, her siblings fought each other to the death
for supremacy. She alone reached her limit... and broke through.

items.name: Melding of the Flesh
explicitMods: -72% to all Elemental Resistances
-4% to all maximum Elemental Resistances
Elemental Resistances are capped by your highest Maximum Elemental Resistance instead
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: "We awoke to a sudden jungle rupturing the valleys of our home.
Grasping limbs coiled around us, into us. We sank into each other,
then rose into the living sky. My family screams alongside me still."

items.name: Watcher's Eye
implicitMods: 21% reduced Effect of Curses on you
You cannot be Cursed with Silence
explicitMods: 4% increased maximum Energy Shield
4% increased maximum Life
6% increased maximum Mana
+7% Chance to Block Attack Damage while affected by Determination
10% of Physical Damage from Hits taken as Lightning Damage while affected by Purity of Elements
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: One by one, they stood their ground against a creature
they had no hope of understanding, let alone defeating,
and one by one, they became a part of it.
